OL,3,CMurder accused in court over death of
OL,4,Cstudent during brawl on Primrose Hill
OL,6,FTwo men have appeared at the Old
OL,7,FBailey accused over the death of a
OL,8,Ffilmmaking student during a brawl on
OL,9,FPrimrose Hill.
OL,11,FFinbar Sullivan, 21, was allegedly
OL,12,Fkicked, punched and fatally stabbed in
OL,13,Fthe early evening on Tuesday April 7
OL,14,Fat the beauty spot's viewpoint in
OL,15,Fnorth London.
OL,17,FThree men have been charged with his
OL,18,Fmurder, and two of them appeared at
OL,19,Fthe Old Bailey on Friday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
