OL,3,CMurder accused in court over death of
OL,4,Cstudent during brawl on Primrose Hill
OL,6,FProsecutor Jennifer Newcomb told the
OL,7,Fcourt that the incident of "extreme
OL,8,Fviolence" happened at about 6.40pm.
OL,10,FIt was allegedly witnessed by numerous
OL,11,Fpassersby, some of whom filmed it on
OL,12,Fmobile phones.
OL,14,FThere were also multiple calls to
OL,15,Fpolice and London Ambulance Service
OL,16,Freporting a fight involving young
OL,17,Fmales, she said.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@IO]
