OL,3,CMurder accused in court over death of
OL,4,Cstudent during brawl on Primrose Hill
OL,6,FMr Sullivan had entered the park at
OL,7,F6.25pm and joined other friends before
OL,8,Fhe allegedly became surrounded by a
OL,9,Fgroup of attackers.
OL,11,FIt is alleged Ernest Boateng, 25,
OL,12,Fkicked Mr Sullivan, taking out his
OL,13,Flegs and causing him to fall to the
OL,14,Fground before he was stabbed.
OL,16,FAlexis Bidace, also 25, is alleged to
OL,17,Fhave punched and kicked Mr Sullivan
OL,18,Falongside a third defendant,
OL,19,FOliuwadamilola Ogunyankinnu, 27.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
