PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776514266
OL,3,CMurder accused in court over death of
OL,4,Cstudent during brawl on Primrose Hill
OL,6,FAnother unnamed male, armed with a
OL,7,Fknife, is alleged to have stabbed him
OL,8,Fin the thigh, causing an
OL,9,F"unsurvivable" injury from which he
OL,10,Fdied at the scene.
OL,12,FBidace and Boateng, both from Enfield,
OL,13,Fnorth London, appeared at the Old
OL,14,FBailey by videolink from Wandsworth
OL,15,Fprison.
OL,17,FThey are charged with murder and spoke
OL,18,Fonly to confirm their identities.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@NO]
