PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776514266
OL,3,CMurder accused in court over death of
OL,4,Cstudent during brawl on Primrose Hill
OL,6,FJudge Angela Rafferty KC ordered them
OL,7,Fto appear for a plea hearing on July 1
OL,8,Falongside co-accused Ogunyankinnu,
OL,9,Falso from Enfield.
OL,11,FA provisional eight-week trial has
OL,12,Fbeen set for April 5 next year. All
OL,13,Fthree defendants have been remanded
OL,14,Finto custody.
OL,16,FMr Sullivan, known as Fin by his
OL,17,Ffriends, was a student at the London
OL,18,FScreen Academy. According to his
OL,19,Ffather, he had gone to Primrose Hill
OL,20,Fto test a new camera he got for his
OL,21,Fbirthday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
