OL,3,CMurder accused in court over death of
OL,4,Cstudent during brawl on Primrose Hill
OL,6,FA fourth man, Khalid Abdulqadir, 18,
OL,7,Fhas been separately charged in
OL,8,Frelation to the same incident.
OL,10,FHe is charged with causing grievous
OL,11,Fbodily harm with intent to a second
OL,12,Falleged victim, violent disorder and
OL,13,Fpossession of a knife.
